SELECT TOP(@__TypedProperty_0) [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[NameDe], [p].[NameRu], [p].[NameTranslateKey]
FROM [ProjectFeature] AS [p]

SELECT TOP(@__TypedProperty_0) [c].[Id], [c].[AddDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Country], [c].[CommentDate], [c].[CommentText], [c].[IsActive], [c].[CommentTextDe], [c].[CommentTextRu], [c].[CommentTextTranslateKey]
FROM [Comment].[Comment] AS [c]
WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)

SELECT TOP(@__TypedProperty_0) [c].[Id], [c].[Name]
FROM [Address].[City] AS [c]
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT DISTINCT 1
    FROM [Project].[Project] AS [p]
    WHERE (([p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)) AND ([p].[IsActive] = CAST(1 AS bit))) AND ([p].[CityId] = [c].[Id]))

SELECT [p].[CityId] AS [Id], [c].[Name], COUNT(*) AS [Total]
FROM [Project].[Project] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Address].[City] AS [c] ON [p].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
WHERE (([p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)) AND ([p].[IsActive] = CAST(1 AS bit))) AND [p].[CityId] IN (7, 35, 50)
GROUP BY [p].[CityId], [c].[Name]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__TypedProperty_2) [p].[Id], [p].[AddDate], [p].[BathroomCount], [p].[CityId], [p].[CurrencyId], [p].[Description], [p].[DescriptionDe], [p].[DescriptionRu], [p].[DescriptionTranslateKey], [p].[DistrictId], [p].[Floor], [p].[GrossArea], [p].[IsActive], [p].[IsFavourite], [p].[IsSold], [p].[NetArea], [p].[Price], [p].[PriceEur], [p].[ProjectDate], [p].[ProjectEndDate], [p].[ProjectNumber], [p].[ProjectStatus], [p].[ProjectTye], [p].[SaloonCount], [p].[SeeClose], [p].[StreetId], [p].[Title], [p].[TitleDe], [p].[TitleRu], [p].[TitleTranslateKey], [p].[TownId], [p].[Year], [p].[ZipCode]
    FROM [Project].[Project] AS [p]
    WHERE ([p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)) AND ([p].[IsActive] = @__TypedProperty_1)
    ORDER BY [p].[AddDate] DESC
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Address].[City] AS [c] ON [t].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Address].[District] AS [d] ON [t].[DistrictId] = [d].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Address].[Street] AS [s] ON [t].[StreetId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Address].[Town] AS [t0] ON [t].[TownId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT @__ImgUrl_0 + [p0].[FileName] AS [c], [p0].[Id], [p0].[ProjectId]
    FROM [ProjectFiles] AS [p0]
    WHERE [p0].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t1] ON ([t].[Id] = [t1].[ProjectId]) AND ([t].[Id] = [t1].[ProjectId])
LEFT JOIN [Feature] AS [f] ON [t].[Id] = [f].[ProjectId]
ORDER BY [t].[AddDate] DESC, [t].[Id], [c].[Id], [d].[Id], [s].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t1].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__TypedProperty_3) [t].[Id], [t].[AddDate], [t].[BathroomCount], [t].[CityId], [t].[CurrencyId], [t].[Description], [t].[DescriptionDe], [t].[DescriptionRu], [t].[DescriptionTranslateKey], [t].[DistrictId], [t].[Floor], [t].[GrossArea], [t].[IsActive], [t].[IsFavourite], [t].[IsSold], [t].[NetArea], [t].[Price], [t].[PriceEur], [t].[ProjectDate], [t].[ProjectEndDate], [t].[ProjectNumber], [t].[ProjectStatus], [t].[ProjectTye], [t].[SaloonCount], [t].[SeeClose], [t].[StreetId], [t].[Title], [t].[TitleDe], [t].[TitleRu], [t].[TitleTranslateKey], [t].[TownId], [t].[Year], [t].[ZipCode]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[AddDate], [p].[BathroomCount], [p].[CityId], [p].[CurrencyId], [p].[Description], [p].[DescriptionDe], [p].[DescriptionRu], [p].[DescriptionTranslateKey], [p].[DistrictId], [p].[Floor], [p].[GrossArea], [p].[IsActive], [p].[IsFavourite], [p].[IsSold], [p].[NetArea], [p].[Price], [p].[PriceEur], [p].[ProjectDate], [p].[ProjectEndDate], [p].[ProjectNumber], [p].[ProjectStatus], [p].[ProjectTye], [p].[SaloonCount], [p].[SeeClose], [p].[StreetId], [p].[Title], [p].[TitleDe], [p].[TitleRu], [p].[TitleTranslateKey], [p].[TownId], [p].[Year], [p].[ZipCode]
        FROM [Project].[Project] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
        ORDER BY [p].[AddDate] DESC
        OFFSET @__TypedProperty_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__TypedProperty_2 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]
    ORDER BY [t].[AddDate] DESC
) AS [t0]
INNER JOIN [Address].[City] AS [c] ON [t0].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Address].[District] AS [d] ON [t0].[DistrictId] = [d].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Address].[Street] AS [s] ON [t0].[StreetId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Address].[Town] AS [t1] ON [t0].[TownId] = [t1].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT @__ImgUrl_0 + [p0].[FileName] AS [c], [p0].[Id], [p0].[ProjectId]
    FROM [ProjectFiles] AS [p0]
    WHERE [p0].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t2] ON ([t0].[Id] = [t2].[ProjectId]) AND ([t0].[Id] = [t2].[ProjectId])
LEFT JOIN [Feature] AS [f] ON [t0].[Id] = [f].[ProjectId]
ORDER BY [t0].[AddDate] DESC, [t0].[Id], [c].[Id], [d].[Id], [s].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t2].[Id]
